Setting up
----------

in your magento tree:

modman init
modman clone magento-credex gitolite@git.credex.us:dev/magento

Unit tests
----------
phpunit --group EmPayTech_CredEx UnitTests.php

Activating the module
---------------------
 - Go to the admin backoffice
 - System > Configuration
 - Sales > Payment Methods
 - Under Credex:
   - Set Enabled to YES
   - Fill in Merchant ID
   - Fill in username
   - Fill in password
